*if p_c1 ='X'.
*   message ' add of the 2 number ' type 'i'.
*
*
*
*  elseif p_c2 = 'X'.
*    message 'substraction of the  2 num ' type 'i'.
*
*
*    elseif p_c3 = 'X'.
*      message 'division of the 2 number ' type 'i'.
